{{tr:hp_campaign_point_1_great_bastion}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_great_bastion_learn_more}}

Fateweaver's minions defile lands under your protection. Leaving them to fester risks a loss of standing with your siblings and father, the Dragon Emperor himself!

