As a [[sl:campaign_daemons_of_chaos]]Daemon Prince[[/sl]] of [[sl:campaign_chaos]]Chaos[[/sl]], you are untethered to the will of the Ruinous Powers. Yet through them great power may be gained... in return for your servitude.

{{tr:hp_campaign_description_daemonic_glory}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_daemonic_glory_add_02}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_daemonic_glory_learn_more}}

Strive to gain further glory from the Gods of [[sl:campaign_chaos]]Chaos[[/sl]]. Through servitude to the Ruinous Powers may be found boundless power.

{{tr:hp_campaign_point_5_daemonic_glory}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_daemonic_glory_learn_more}}

[[sl:campaign_daemons_of_chaos]]Daemon Princes[[/sl]] differ from other daemonic creatures as they were once mortal - a soul still withers within them. This also allows them, and you, agency over their form. Continue your evolution into a shape that shall please you.

[[sl_tooltip:campaign_daemonic_gifts]]Daemonic Gifts[[/sl_tooltip]] are unlocked as [[sl:campaign_daemonic_glory]]Daemonic Glory[[/sl]] is earned with each Chaos God.

