Select an army or [[img:icon_hero]][[/img]]Hero and right-click a Skull Pile when one appears to harvest Skulls from it.

{{tr:hp_campaign_skulls_learn_more}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_point_5_skulls}}

Send Skulls to the Skull Throne to please [[sl:campaign_khorne]]Khorne[[/sl]] and gain his mighty favour.

{{tr:hp_campaign_skulls_learn_more}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_description_skulls}}

{{tr:hp_campaign_point_1_skulls}}

