The [[sl:campaign_khorne]]Blood God[[/sl]]'s thirst for Skulls cannot be quenched. Bring Skulls! Bring them now!

Blood for the Blood God! Skulls for the Skull Throne!

{{tr:hp_campaign_skulls_learn_more}}

